      <a class="logo-wrapper w-nav-brand" href="https://www.buttonjoy.com"><img class="logo-img" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 77vw, 232.5px" src="images/buttonjoy-logo-grey.png" srcset="images/buttonjoy-logo-grey-p-500x121.png 500w, images/buttonjoy-logo-grey.png 665w" width="232.5">
